longBusinessSummary: Record Resources Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of lithium and gold properties in Canada. The company holds an option agreement to acquire a 100% interest in the Doran lithium property covering an area of 3,474 hectares located in northwestern Ontario. It also holds interest in the Grenfell gold property covering an area of approximately 6.7 square kilometers located towards the northwest of the Town of Kirkland Lake, Ontario; and an option agreement to acquire a 100% interest in the Four Nations property, which consists of five claim blocks comprising 5.2 square kilometers in the Grenfell Township. In addition, the company holds interest in the Kenogami East, Amikougami, and Otto gold exploration properties located in Kirkland Lake, Ontario. The company was formerly known as Silk Road Energy Inc. and changed its name to Record Resources Inc. in April 2023. Record Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Montreal, Canada.
